WEBVTT

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.635
Last time on Sonic X,

00:00:01.635 --> 00:00:03.504
Chris was trapped on Space Colony ARK,

00:00:03.504 --> 00:00:05.372
but Sonic rocketed to his rescue!

00:00:05.372 --> 00:00:07.641
Soon, Eggman ambushed the hapless hedgehog

00:00:07.641 --> 00:00:09.176
and gave our hero the heave-ho.

00:00:09.176 --> 00:00:11.211
The devious doc issued an ultimatum.

00:00:11.211 --> 00:00:12.880
If he wasn't made supreme ruler,

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:14.481
he'd pulverize the planet!

00:00:14.481 --> 00:00:16.416
But when Eggman fired up the Eclipse Cannon,

00:00:16.416 --> 00:00:18.485
he got a blastĂ˘from the past!

00:00:18.485 --> 00:00:20.687
A recording from his grandfather,
Professor Robotnik,

00:00:20.687 --> 00:00:23.123
revealed that he had his own
plan to wipe out the world.

00:00:23.123 --> 00:00:25.325
Can Sonic save the globe from destruction?

00:00:25.325 --> 00:00:27.027
Or will Robotnik wreak his revenge?

00:00:27.027 --> 00:00:29.196
Find out next on Sonic X!

